name: Elon Musk Incorporated
description:
Elon is about to make a new shipping company of his own, and there's no better workers than robots, you can command them to deliver it through the factory,
there are 5 endings, each ending depends how many packages you deliver under
a MINUTE.
DEVNOTE:
try selecting the robot with their shadows, the collision box is in there, I'm still new to isometric perspective.
If the timer hits 60, the game is over, you can stop it before it does with Space Bar.
If the robots collide, they're automatically disabled and cannot continue working.
